        "timestamp": "2022-05-07 06:28:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nHi all,\n\nPlease kindly help to review the patch.\n\nIn the last patch, I thought I've fixed the healthcheck problem of Holmes. But after I looked through the recent logs, I found that I missed to handle exceptions on a conditional branch, which make the healthcheck still fail.\n\nAs the problem could only be reproduced in the daily healthcheck environment, it takes a little bit long time for us to validate if the changes work. That's why I'm still submitting changes at this very moment.\n\nI know it's already over the deadline for merging changes into the oom repository, but I strongly recommend that we merge the patch as soon as possible.\n\nThanks,\nGuangrong",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
